Entries.default: "What do we have here?" A young man dressed in skin-tight leathers gives you a quick once over. He must like what he sees, because he smiles wide, his lips just parted.
"Missing me, were you?" A smug smile brings dimples to his pale cheeks.
"How can I ease your troubles, friend?"
"Right this way..." He takes you by the arm and leads you gently to a waiting table.
"I surprise and delight the clientele." He winks.
"I got other skills, of course, should you be looking. And all for a measly two hundred pires!"
"My specialty's oils - full body rubdowns, right, fit to leave you limber, clear-headed, and free of the stresses of hard living."
